com.st.olm.cq.sling.models.containers

Class ResourceCategory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.st.olm.cq.sling.models.containers.ResourceCategory

  • public class ResourceCategory
extends Object
    Model object for resource category configuration. Initialized from objects under /etc/stconfig/widgets/resources/resources_root and extra data added from resource query results.
    Author:
    Ken Casey
